                                                                           /-- KCaloJetProducer
                     KManualMultiProducer ------ KManualMultiLVProducer --*
                    /       \                   /                          \-- KPartonProducer
                   |         KVertexProducer   |
                   |        /                  |
KBaseMultiProducer *   KCommonVectorProducer   |
        ^          |        \                  |
        |          |         KCommonLVProducer *                           /-- KTrackProducer
 KBaseProducerWP    \                           \                         |
        ^            KRegexMultiProducer ---*--- KRegexMultiLVProducer ---*--- KLorentzProducer
        |                                   |                             |
  KBaseProducer                             |\-- KMETProducer              \-- KMuonProducer
                                            |
                                            \--- KTowerProducer

